data.text:
SKU 9940036

Be comfortable by wearing the Clarks® Walkford Band sandal. Crafted from classic black leather, this slip-on profile ensures easy on/off. The bouncy cushioned footbed provides lasting comfort for sun-soaked days, while the slip-resistant sole offers stability. Clarks' quality craftsmanship is evident, and a subtle branding icon completes this season's staple.

Leather upper.

Mesh lining.

Rubber insole.

Synthetic rubber outsole.

Imported.
